    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions like @Compendium[pf1.spells.tjog6bufg5b08lvq]{Charm Person}, except that mass <em>charm person</em> affects a number of humanoid creatures whose combined Hit Dice don't exceed twice your level. If there are more potential targets than you can affect, you choose them one at a time until you reach the limit of HD you can affect. If you cast mass <em>charm person</em> on only one creature, you ignore the spell's HD limit.</p>",
